  "desc": "<p>A businesswoman and researcher who specializes in Liyue Mercantilism. Despite rigorously researching and consolidating a successful business strategy, she laments that her shop has never had the honor of Rex Lapis' personal patronage. It is said that all shops that have welcomed Rex Lapis' presence and approval have all become famous household names.</p>",
